    Compactor

    public class MRCompactor
extends Object
implements Compactor
    MapReduce-based Compactor. Compaction will run on each qualified Dataset under COMPACTION_INPUT_DIR.

      • datasetAlreadyCompacted

        public static boolean datasetAlreadyCompacted(FileSystem fs,
                                              Dataset dataset,
                                              boolean renameSourceEnable)
        A Dataset is considered already compacted if either condition is true: 1) When completion file strategy is used, a compaction completion means there is a file named COMPACTION_COMPLETE_FILE_NAME in its Dataset.outputPath(). 2) When renaming source directory strategy is used, a compaction completion means source directories Dataset.inputPaths() contains at least one directory which has been renamed to something with COMPACTION_RENAME_SOURCE_DIR_SUFFIX.
